## Game Jam Entries

### Js13kGames

[Js13kGames](js13kgames) is a JavaScript coding competition with a
file size limit of 13 kilobytes.

* ### Pronto
	<a href="http://pronto.markusfisch.de/"><img class="Screenshot"
		src="screenshots/pronto.png" alt="Pronto"/></a>
	Simple reaction game for [Js13kGames][js13kgames] 2018 "offline".
	6923 bytes (51%).

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in September 2018</span>$(loc ../Pronto:submission src.js)</p>

	+ [Play](http://pronto.markusfisch.de/)
	+ [Entry](https://js13kgames.com/entries/pronto)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/Pronto)
* ### Lost Treasures
	<a href="http://hhsw.de/sites/LostTreasures/"><img class="Screenshot"
		src="screenshots/lost_treasures.png" alt="Lost Treasures"/></a>
	Dive to find coins for [Js13kGames][js13kgames] 2017 "Lost".
	7928 bytes (59%).

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in September 2017</span>$(loc ../LostTreasures:submission src.js)</p>

	+ [Play](http://hhsw.de/sites/LostTreasures/)
	+ [Entry](http://js13kgames.com/entries/lost-treasures)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/LostTreasures)
* ### Glitch Yeagers
	<a href="http://hhsw.de/sites/GlitchYeagers/"><img class="Screenshot"
		src="screenshots/glitch_yeagers.png" alt="Glitch Yeagers"/></a>
