### 0h Game Jam

[0h Game Jam][0hgame] is a coding competition that takes place during
[DST hour shift](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daylight_saving_time).

* ### Huh
	Click on a free spot to survive. Made for [0h Game Jam][0hgame] 2014.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in October 2014</span>$(loc ../huh:submission)</p>

	+ [Play](http://hhsw.de/sites/proto/huh/)
	+ [Timelapse](https://vimeo.com/110055282)

